  "detailed_description": "<h1>8/15 Koraku released!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/fe972095697dfff953ee838e7e630352.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=240 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/fe972095697dfff953ee838e7e630352.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/fe972095697dfff953ee838e7e630352.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/82a8748e0783c4fd70e9d88cce97c772.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=346 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/82a8748e0783c4fd70e9d88cce97c772.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/82a8748e0783c4fd70e9d88cce97c772.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/e9940c54ade5977a7f72a11289e599a0.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=418 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/e9940c54ade5977a7f72a11289e599a0.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/e9940c54ade5977a7f72a11289e599a0.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/f090091732c7032e5cf41ca6d9b48448.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=418 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/f090091732c7032e5cf41ca6d9b48448.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/f090091732c7032e5cf41ca6d9b48448.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/903d0bcf66bd7e6df35b011a646cccde.avif?t=1771229941\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras_big/903d0bcf66bd7e6df35b011a646cccde.avif?t=1771229941 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE A VIRTUAL WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/c075679faa04c411865856fe589fc47b.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/c075679faa04c411865856fe589fc47b.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/c075679faa04c411865856fe589fc47b.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Battle your way through unique and beautiful locations. Packed with challenge monsters and enormous bosses bent on taking you out, don’t give them the satisfaction!</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/924d5d1f1afe55411bcf4d555700a9b9.webp?t=1771229941\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/924d5d1f1afe55411bcf4d555700a9b9.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=252 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick one of six characters each with unique abilities and battle styles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/cfe6f8fc5369b42aff93709cc14b22e5.avif?t=1771229941\" width=615 height=220 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY SOLO OR CO-OP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself by taking on enemies alone, or with up to four of your friends online and battle cooperatively!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
