_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/25a6b63b7691fd7a276d02c1251a5e4a.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.poster.avif?t=1771229941\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.webm?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425000/extras/bb93532c47788492856d1f69306d0c8b.mp4?t=1771229941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
